  "detailed_description": "The peace and quiet of everyday life will be dispelled like an illusion after the appearance of a mysterious stranger on the tail with an enemy army. <br>Unpredictable circumstances, interesting puzzles and situations that can change the course of events in a split second, go through a difficult path in this struggle for your own home and freedom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/dd441dba2a902573e221e94241a1c959.poster.avif?t=1644821851\" width=614 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/dd441dba2a902573e221e94241a1c959.webm?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/dd441dba2a902573e221e94241a1c959.mp4?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense</h2>Build, upgrade, and take part directly in first-person battles. Destroy waves of enemies that are coming at you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/2ca2172f54d4d4cd4b12bfd22f9066d1.poster.avif?t=1644821851\" width=614 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/2ca2172f54d4d4cd4b12bfd22f9066d1.webm?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/2ca2172f54d4d4cd4b12bfd22f9066d1.mp4?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle levels</h2>Not only destroy enemies, but also complete puzzles to advance further in the story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/c8b107c17856ce356ac27c21a587c277.poster.avif?t=1644821851\" width=614 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/c8b107c17856ce356ac27c21a587c277.webm?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/c8b107c17856ce356ac27c21a587c277.mp4?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss battle</h2>Fight your enemy one-on-one. Defeat him and protect your home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/ba9b31b524f8c036759f16c8a3ebb1f3.poster.avif?t=1644821851\" width=614 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/ba9b31b524f8c036759f16c8a3ebb1f3.webm?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691300/extras/ba9b31b524f8c036759f16c8a3ebb1f3.mp4?t=1644821851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
